Transverse,is,a,software,as,a,service,company,that,provides,businesses,a,way,to,automate,billing,and,manage,their,customer,subscriptions,The,Transverse,Tract,REST,API,lets,developers,integrate,their,applications,with,the,Tract,service,by,making,REST,requests,to,the,API,The,API,uses,HTTP,Basic,Authentication